This is an Application I am making for TCT to use. Using this is a learning experiance, practice, and to help out the place I work.
It is a simple application that lets you create questionares or polls and you can invite users to join your poll and respond. 
I am utilizing firebase firestore for my backend to save time and learn more about it.

I used Kotlin to start learning kotlin, then fell in love. Now I am dedicated to gaining a full understanding of how it works.


Future updates will let you access from a browser and interact with the same data.
